OL,3,CBoy, 14, becomes 11th person to die in
OL,4,Cwater during record heatwave
OL,6,FPolice said: "The 14-year-old boy's
OL,7,Ffamily have been informed and offered
OL,8,Fsupport; our thoughts are with them at
OL,9,Fthis extremely difficult time.
OL,11,F"The death is being treated as
OL,12,Funexplained but not suspicious and our
OL,13,Finvestigation is ongoing."
OL,15,FThe body of another teenage boy was
OL,16,Ffound on Thursday in Kent after
OL,17,Femergency services were called to
OL,18,Freports of concerns for a swimmer in
OL,19,Fthe Galley Hill Road area of
OL,20,FSwanscombe in Kent on Wednesday
OL,21,Fafternoon.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
