OL,3,CBoy, 14, becomes 11th person to die in
OL,4,Cwater during record heatwave
OL,6,F"He will be truly missed. He was the
OL,7,Flife and soul of our lives," they said.
OL,9,FHis body was retrieved by emergency
OL,10,Fservices at 7.50pm on Tuesday
OL,11,Ffollowing a large-scale search
OL,12,Foperation.
OL,14,FEarlier on Wednesday, the body of a
OL,15,Fteenage boy was recovered from Hawley
OL,16,FLake near Blackwater, in Hampshire,
OL,17,Fafter he was reported missing on
OL,18,FTuesday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
