OL,3,CBoy, 14, becomes 11th person to die in
OL,4,Cwater during record heatwave
OL,6,FFormal identification has not yet
OL,7,Ftaken place, but Hampshire and Isle of
OL,8,FWight Police say the missing boy's
OL,9,Ffamily have been notified.
OL,11,FIt follows police finding another body
OL,12,Fduring the search for a 17-year-old
OL,13,Fboy last seen at a lake in Cheshire.
OL,15,FA Cheshire Constabulary spokesperson
OL,16,Fsaid officers were called to reports
OL,17,Fof a missing boy last seen in the
OL,18,Fwater at Pickmere Lake, near Northwich.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
