OL,3,CBoy, 14, becomes 11th person to die in
OL,4,Cwater during record heatwave
OL,6,FThree teenage boys and one girl also
OL,7,Fdied in separate incidents over the
OL,8,FBank Holiday weekend after going into
OL,9,Fthe water in Lincolnshire, South
OL,10,FYorkshire, West Yorkshire, and
OL,11,FWarwickshire.
OL,13,FReco Puttock, 13, was pronounced dead
OL,14,Fin hospital after he was pulled from a
OL,15,Freservoir at Leadbeater Dam, Halifax,
OL,16,Fjust after 3pm on Monday, West
OL,17,FYorkshire Police said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
