OL,3,CBoy, 14, becomes 11th person to die in
OL,4,Cwater during record heatwave
OL,6,FHours later, the body of a teenage
OL,7,Fgirl was recovered from Kingsbury
OL,8,FWater Park, just south of Tamworth,
OL,9,FStaffordshire, on Monday evening
OL,10,Ffollowing a police search.
OL,12,FDespite the efforts of emergency
OL,13,Fservices, she was pronounced dead at
OL,14,Fthe scene, Atherstone and Coleshill
OL,15,FPolice said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
