OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780038278
OL,3,CBoy, 14, becomes 11th person to die in
OL,4,Cwater during record heatwave
OL,6,FThe relatives were brought to shore by
OL,7,Fmembers of the public during the
OL,8,Fincident.
OL,10,FThe deaths have prompted the Royal
OL,11,FLife Saving Society (RLSS) to issue a
OL,12,Fwarning, saying it sees a "heightened
OL,13,Frisk of drowning when air temperatures
OL,14,Fare higher".
OL,16,FThe Met Office said Tuesday was the
OL,17,FUK's hottest day in May on record,
OL,18,Fbreaking records set the previous two
OL,19,Fdays.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
